  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>ATTENTION </strong>independent free spirits who thrive on friendship, community and new experiences!</p><p><br /></p><p>M Social Singapore is characteristically scouting for the curious, the explorers and the ones who dare to dream. We lust sanguine individuals who are expressive with a touch of creativity. Leave the stiff handshakes behind. Let’s make some memories together. Join our M Socialite movement.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wait no further, M Social Casting Call – <strong>Technician</strong> is now open!</p><p><br /></p><p>The role reports to Duty Engineer and <strong>YOU</strong> are responsible for the following;-</p><ul><li>Maintain the day to day engineering operations of the hotel</li><li>Perform routine preventive maintenance</li><li>Perform repairs timely and efficiently</li><li>Ability to work under pressure situations and exercise good judgements</li><li>Ability to read and understand test equipment, measuring devices, and safety manuals</li><li>To be available for any emergencies and act in an engineering capacity to protect guests and associates and preserve the building and its systems during the emergency.</li><li>Maintains the hotel facility and related equipment in a safe and efficient manner</li><li>To carry out any other duties and responsibilities as assigned</li></ul><p>So what’s the requirements?</p><ul><li>NITEC / Higher NITEC in Building Technician or equivalent.</li><li>At least one year of experience in facilities maintenance.</li><li>Willing to do night shifts</li></ul><p>Time and tide wait for no man, hurry send in your application NOW!</p><p>Human Resources</p><p>M Social Singapore</p><p>90 Robertson Quay</p><p>Singapore 238259</p><p><em>e-mail address: jolie.yee@millenniumhotels.com</em></p><p><em>We apologise that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</em></p>",
